Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:04.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Abans que fos\Nen Conan Edogawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:07.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"la Ran em va dir de quedar\Na l'Aquari de Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"per preparar l'anomenat 'projecte\Ndels dos amants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que es retroben a l'aquari\Nper casualitat',
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que havia de servir perquè els seus pares separats es reconciliessin."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però, llavors..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Les línies de la mà són metxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,la línia del cor encén el foc\Nde la deducció."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:33.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Vídeos gravats amb el mòbil\Nal passadís subaquàtic."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un personatge curiós revela\Nla veritat."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:37.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,kanjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kanpeki ni lose control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,baguru utto ushisa ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:54.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Heki eki wakatteru.\NSutansu, sutansu, sutansu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari ID
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:00.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,gen'in suisoku shite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:06.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,tousou hon'nou zenkai\Numaku wa waraenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:09.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sutensu, sutensu, sutensu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:13.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Chansu tsukamasu sutansu, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:17.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Reeru no nai michi Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:23.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Dare ni mo\Ntomerarenai kono kimochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NKokoro ga sawagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:32.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NOwarasenaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mirai ga mieru\NI'm gonna be your dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh! Buttobe your dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:50.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NKokoro ga sawagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NOwarasenaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mirai ga mieru\NI'm gonna be your dynamite.
